des:
Quick recipe for your special needs. Jen offers a pleasant help, suggesting you recipes, and guiding you through their preparation.
Try it by saying "Alexa, launch Jen carrot" or ask for a recipe, for example "Alexa, tell me a vegan lunch recipe."
Enjoy Jen's company, never more cooking alone!
